An example of the fixed-point combinator in Duck:<p><pre><code>  function fixed_point(f)
    function curry(g, i)
      function recurse(j)
        return g(g, j)
      end
      return f(recurse, i)
    end

    function apply(k)
      return curry(curry, k)
    end

    return apply
  end</code></pre>
